# Practical Publishing Actions

Add a new post or return to the posts list after creating or updating one.

## Features

* Add a button to add a new post after saving/publishing.
* Add a second button to return to the post list after saving/publishing.

## Usage

1. Copy the `practical-publishing-actions` directory into your `wp-content/plugins` directory
2. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' screen in WordPress

